        <source> Enter the verification code sent to <x id="START_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;strong class=&quot;text-on-surface&quot;&gt;"/><x id="INTERPOLATION" equiv-text="{{ challenge()?.email }}"/><x id="CLOSE_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;/strong&gt;"/> to continue. </source>
        <target> Ingresa el código de verificación enviado a <x id="START_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;strong class=&quot;text-on-surface&quot;&gt;"/><x id="INTERPOLATION" equiv-text="{{ challenge()?.email }}"/><x id="CLOSE_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;/strong&gt;"/> para continuar. </target>
